text: Madeleine Arthur (born March 10, 1997) is a Canadian actress. She is known for her role as young Willa Warren in the ABC drama series The Family. She played Jane Keane, the daughter of Amy Adams' character, in Tim Burton's biographical movie Big Eyes (2014). Arthur also has had guest roles in The Killing, The Tomorrow People, and Supernatural. == References == Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian actors
